                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 lotte-red-text">1. Filter Unqualified Leads</h3>
                    <p class="mb-4">To reduce processing costs for ineligible "freelancer" applications, implement a pre-screening step on the registration form.</p>
                    <div class="border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <p class="font-semibold">Proposed Solution:</p>
                        <div class="mt-2 flex items-center space-x-4">
