                                <select id="job" name="job" class="mt-1 block w-full pl-3 pr-10 py-2 text-base border-gray-300 focus:outline-none focus:ring-lotte-red focus:border-lotte-red sm:text-sm rounded-md">
                                    <option>Salaried Employee</option>
                                    <option>Business Owner</option>
                                    <option>Freelancer</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                         <div class="mt-4 flex items-center bg-red-100 border-l-4 border-red-500 text-red-700 p-3 rounded-md">
                            <span class="text-2xl mr-3">🚫</span>
                            <p class="text-sm">If "Freelancer" is selected, show message: "We are sorry, but Lotte Finance does not currently support loans for freelancers."</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 lotte-red-text">2. Create Dedicated Landing Pages</h3>
                    <p class="mb-4">Improve relevance and Google Ads Quality Score by creating specific landing pages for major SEM keyword groups.</p>
                     <div class="border-2 border-dashed border-gray-300 rounded-lg p-4">
                        <p class="font-semibold">Current Flow:</p>
                        <div class="text-center p-2 mt-2 rounded-md bg-yellow-100">"Salary Loan" Ad ➜ Generic LP</div>
                        <div class="text-center p-2 mt-2 rounded-md bg-yellow-100">"Consumer Loan" Ad ➜ Generic LP</div>
                        
                        <p class="font-semibold mt-4">Proposed Flow:</p>
                        <div class="text-center p-2 mt-2 rounded-md bg-green-100">"Salary Loan" Ad ➜ **Salary Loan LP**</div>
                        <div class="text-center p-2 mt-2 rounded-md bg-green-100">"Consumer Loan" Ad ➜ **Consumer Loan LP**</div>
                        
                         <div class="mt-4 flex items-center bg-green-100 border-l-4 border-green-500 text-green-700 p-3 rounded-md">
                            <span class="text-2xl mr-3">📈</span>
                            <p class="text-sm"><strong>Benefit:</strong> Higher relevance leads to lower costs, better ad positions, and increased conversion rates.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

