                <p><strong>Benefit:</strong> By implementing value-based bidding strategies like `Target ROAS` or `Maximize Conversion Value` in Google Ads, the algorithm will automatically bid higher for users more likely to reach the `Disbursement` stage, and lower for users who only show potential for an initial lead. This dramatically improves the return on ad spend (ROAS) and focuses the budget on what truly matters.</p>
