        <section id="summary" class="section-card">
            <h2 class="text-center">Summary & Recommendations</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-8 mt-8">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">Key Learnings</h3>
                    
                    <h4 class="lotte-red-text">Channel Performance</h4>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-4 mb-4">
                        <li><strong>SEM</strong> is the most efficient channel for final disbursement (19% Cost/Disb) despite higher lead costs.</li>
                        <li><strong>GPM</strong> provides the cheapest leads but is least efficient for disbursement (33% Cost/Disb), suggesting lower lead quality.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4 class="lotte-red-text">Audience & Targeting</h4>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-4 mb-4">
                        <li><strong>Top Keywords:</strong> Brand ("Lotte Finance") and niche product ("Vay Bảo Hiểm Nhân Thọ") keywords are most effective.</li>
                        <li><strong>Underperforming Keywords:</strong> Indirect keywords ("buy car", "fix house") do not receive significant distribution due to low relevance.</li>
                        <li><strong>Top Audiences:</strong> Retargeting is the most efficient audience (13.7% Cost/Disb), followed by the performance-based Female audience (22.05%).</li>
                         <li><strong>Poor Audiences:</strong> Combining past performance with normal TA dilutes quality and is least effective (33.69%).</li>
                    </ul>
                     
                    <h4 class="lotte-red-text">Creative & Landing Page</h4>
                     <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-4 mb-4">
                        <li><strong>Banner Pack 1</strong>, which combines authentic imagery with clear offers, is significantly more effective than the text-only Pack 2.</li>
                        <li>The **Normal Landing Page** yields higher quality leads and better final conversion than the Simple LP, despite a higher initial CPL.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4">Action Plan</h3>

                    <h4 class="text-gray-800">Channel Strategy</h4>
                     <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-4 mb-4">
                        <li>Allocate the majority of the budget to **SEM** due to its proven efficiency. Limit budget for GPM.</li>
                        <li>**SEM:** Expand campaigns with Brand and Niche Product keywords, directing traffic to the Normal LP or new dedicated LPs.</li>
                        <li>**GDE/GPM:** Use primarily for **Retargeting** and Brand Awareness campaigns, not for new lead generation.</li>
                    </ul>

                     <h4 class="text-gray-800">Audience Targeting</h4>
                     <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-4 mb-4">
                        <li>Allocate budget towards top-performing keyword groups.</li>
                        <li>Prioritize and increase budget for **Retargeting** campaigns.</li>
                        <li><strong>Implement Advanced Targeting:</strong> Use Lookalike and Custom Intent audiences in Google Ads to find high-value users.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h4 class="text-gray-800">Creative Strategy</h4>
                     <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-4 mb-4">
                        <li>Focus budget exclusively on **Banner Pack 1**.</li>
                        <li>Produce more banners and videos featuring authentic human imagery tailored to specific audiences and offers.</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4 class="text-gray-800">Landing Page & Data Optimization</h4>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 pl-4">
                        <li>Create **Dedicated LPs** for top keyword groups to improve Quality Score and conversion rates.</li>
                        <li>Use the **Normal LP** for new lead acquisition campaigns.</li>
                        <li>**Filter at the Source:** Add a "freelancer" filter to the registration form.</li>
                        <li>**Optimize Data Systems:** Integrate CRM data with ad platforms for deeper, value-based bidding and unify fragmented data sources.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
